, "currencyservice-0", "currencyservice-1", "currencyservice-2", "emailservice-0", "emailservice-1", "emailservice-2", "frontend-0", "frontend-1", "frontend-2", "paymentservice-0", "paymentservice-1", "paymentservice-2", "productcatalogservice-0", "productcatalogservice-1", "productcatalogservice-2", "recommendationservice-0", "recommendationservice-1", "recommendationservice-2", "redis-cart-0", "shippingservice-0", "shippingservice-1", "shippingservice-2"], "metric_name": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes", "node_memory_usage_rate", "pod_cpu_usage", "rrt", "rrt_max"]}, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["checkoutservice-1", "emailservice-1", "shippingservice-0", "recommendationservice-2", "productcatalogservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["shippingservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "cartservice-0", "productcatalogservice-2", "frontend-0", "paymentservice-1", "adservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["frontend-2", "currencyservice-1", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["paymentservice-2", "currencyservice-0", "cartservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["checkoutservice-2", "emailservice-2", "productcatalogservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["currencyservice-2", "adservice-1", "emailservice-0", "frontend-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["redis-cart-0", "adservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "recommendationservice-0", "shippingservice-1", "cartservice-2", "productcatalogservice-2"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault was detected from 2025-06-09T09:10:42Z to 2025-06-09T09:25:42Z. Please analyze its root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-09 09:10:42+00:00 to 2025-06-09 09:25:42+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["checkoutservice-1", "emailservice-1", "shippingservice-0", "recommendationservice-2", "productcatalogservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["shippingservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "cartservice-0", "productcatalogservice-2", "frontend-0", "paymentservice-1", "adservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["frontend-2", "currencyservice-1", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["paymentservice-2", "currencyservice-0", "cartservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["checkoutservice-2", "emailservice-2", "productcatalogservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["currencyservice-2", "adservice-1", "emailservice-0", "frontend-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["redis-cart-0", "adservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "recommendationservice-0", "shippingservice-1", "cartservice-2", "productcatalogservice-2"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes", "node_memory_usage_rate", "pod_cpu_usage", "rrt", "rrt_max"], "log_analysis_findings": "从提供的日志数据中提取以下信息进行分析。\n\n### 错误模式识别\n\n- **前端服务错误**:\n  - 频繁出现的报错信息为 `\"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = Unknown desc = \"`, 来自 `frontend` 服务。日志显示多个请求失败，无法获取广告。这些错误通常是由于目标服务不可访问或其返回错误导致。\n  \n- **广告服务异常**:\n  - 在 `adservice` 服务中，我们发现了多个异常日志，例如 `\"Exception in thread \\\"grpc-default-executor-8140\\\" java.lang.Error: Injected error\"`, `Agent failed to start!`, `Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once` 等。这些异常指向广告服务的内部异常和可能的配置问题。\n\n### 识别异常组件与原因\n\n综合日志数据分析，主要问题似乎出现在 `adservice` 服务上，导致 `frontend` 无法成功获取广告。\n\n### 提取的关键词\n\n- 错误类型: `rpc error`, `Unknown desc`, `java.lang.Error`, `Agent failed to start`\n- 日志标签: `AdService-getRandomAds-exception`\n- 异常名称: `InvocationTargetException`, `Inject trigger into`\n\n### JSON 输出\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\n    \"rpc error\",\n    \"Unknown desc\",\n    \"java.lang.Error\",\n    \"Agent failed to start\",\n    \"AdService-getRandomAds-exception\",\n    \"InvocationTargetException\",\n    \"Inject trigger into\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"广告服务出现了多个异常和配置问题，导致前端服务无法成功获取广告。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"日志显示了 adservice 出现 Rpc 错误和多次加载代理失败的异常。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n在当前的错误日志中，我们能够很明显的看到 adservice 服务可能是根本原因，它导致了 frontend 服务无法获取其需要的广告数据。这个问题可能与 adservice 的内部异常和配置相关。我们建议进一步检查和修复 adservice 的运行和配置问题。", "trace_analysis_findings": "根据获得的数据，我们能够识别出异常调用链及其潜在的原因。以下是发现的几个显著异常调用链：\n\n1. **Cartservice与Redis的调用异常**：\n   - **调用链**: `cartservice-2->redis`\n   - **操作**: `HGET`\n   - **正常平均耗时**: 1553.16 ms\n   - **异常平均耗时**: 19470.0 ms\n   - **延迟倍数**: 12.54 倍\n   - **次数**: 2 次\n\n2. **Checkoutservice与Cartservice的调用异常**：\n   - **调用链**: `checkoutservice-2->cartservice-0`\n   - **操作**: `POST /hipstershop.CartService/GetCart`\n   - **正常平均耗时**: 2495.93 ms\n   - **异常平均耗时**: 12413.13 ms\n   - **延迟倍数**: 4.97 倍\n   - **次数**: 2 次\n\n3. **Frontend与Cartservice的调用异常**：\n   - **调用链**: `frontend-2->cartservice-0`\n   - **操作**: `POST /hipstershop.CartService/AddItem`\n   - **正常平均耗时**: 3982.01 ms\n   - **异常平均耗时**: 37343.75 ms\n   - **延迟倍数**: 9.38 倍\n   - **次数**: 2 次\n\n4. **Frontend自身操作异常**：\n   - **调用链**: `frontend-2->frontend-2`\n   - **操作**: `hipstershop.CartService/AddItem`\n   - **正常平均耗时**: 5267.97 ms\n   - **异常平均耗时**: 38840.75 ms\n   - **延迟倍数**: 7.37 倍\n   - **次数**: 2 次\n\n5. **ProductCatalogService异常**：\n   - **调用链**: `checkoutservice-2->productcatalogservice-2`\n   - **操作**: `hipstershop.ProductCatalogService/GetProduct`\n   - **正常平均耗时**: 10547.94 ms\n   - **异常平均耗时**: 20507.0 ms\n   - **延迟倍数**: 1.94 倍\n   - **次数**: 1 次\n\n基于这些调用链上的延迟数据，我们可以提出以下假设凌：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"cartservice-2->redis\", \"checkoutservice-2->cartservice-0\", \"frontend-2->cartservice-0\", \"...\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Redis操作（HGET）在异常时段的响应时间平均增加了约12.54倍。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"调用Cartservice异常时段的响应时间平均增加了约4.97倍。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"调用Cartservice异常时段的响应时间平均增加了约9.38倍。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ProductCatalogService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Checkoutservice调用该服务时响应时间略有异常增加。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n这些被识别出的异常可能与系统压力有关，尤其是涉及到Redis和Cartservice的调用。这些异常调用链可能会为后续的故障排查提供宝贵的线索。", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据分析结果，我识别出以下显著异常调用链：\n\n1. **Node 异常**\n   - *Component*: `aiops-k8s-03`\n   - *异常指标*: `node_memory_usage_rate`, `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes`\n   - *变化数据*:\n     - `node_memory_usage_rate` 从 34.44 上升到 52.62，变化率 41.76%\n     - `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes` 从 10461671424.0 降到 7412334592.0，变化率 34.12%\n   - *Reason*: 该节点的内存使用率显著增加。\n\n2. **Pod 异常影响**\n   - *Component*: `paymentservice-1` 在 `aiops-k8s-03`\n   - *异常指标*: `rrt_max`\n   - *变化数据*: 从 2893.0 上升到 3183.0，变化率 9.55%，最大值变化从 4897.8 到 65258.7\n   - *Reason*: 该Pod所在节点内存压力可能影响了服务响应时间。\n\n3. **Pod 生命周期异常信号**\n   - *Component*: `redis-cart-0`\n   - *异常指标*: `pod_cpu_usage`\n   - *变化数据*: 最大值从 0.07 到 0.11，变化率 43.4%\n   - *Reason*: `pod_cpu_usage` 增加可能指示该 Pod 资源使用上涨。\n\n4. **服务性能异常**\n   - *Component*: `shippingservice-2`\n   - *异常指标*: `rrt_max`\n   - *变化数据*: 从 2513.0 上升到 3207.0，变化率 24.27%，最大值从 7952.08 到 49187.1\n   - *Reason*: 响应时间显著增加，可能由于节点内存消耗压力影响。\n\n5. **客户端错误率异常**\n   - *Component*: `adservice-0`\n   - *异常指标*: `client_error_ratio`, `error_ratio`\n   - *变化数据*: 错误率在最大值时变化 80.35%\n   - *Reason*: 客户端错误率增加表明该服务可能存在请求处理方面的问题。\n\n总结：主要的问题在于节点 `aiops-k8s-03` 的内存压力显著增加，影响了该节点上的多个服务性能表现。此外，`redis-cart-0` 的 CPU 使用上升也提供了显著的异常信号。所有检测到的异常指标如下。\n\n### 输出格式 (JSON)\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"node_memory_usage_rate\",\n    \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"error_ratio\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-03\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_usage_rate 急剧升高以及 node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes 显著下降。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate 从 34.44 上升到 52.62；node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes 从 10461671424.0 降到 7412334592.0。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max 异常上升，影响服务响应时间。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max 从 2893.0 上升到 3183.0，最大值从 4897.8 到 65258.7。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_cpu_usage 增加标志着资源使用异常。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage 最大值从 0.07 增加到 0.11。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max 异常上升，表明服务响应时间增加。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max 从 2513.0 上升到 3207.0，最大值从 7952.08 到 49187.1。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"client_error_ratio 上升，表明可能存在请求处理问题。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio 和 error_ratio 在最大值时变化 80.35%。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n通过分析以上数据，建议进一步关注节点 `aiops-k8s-03` 的内存使用以确定是否需要改善，并评估 `paymentservice-1` 和 `redis-cart-0` 的具体情况。"}
